<plot>The short in the "Unusual Occupations" series (production number L6-4) features Lila Finn, Hollywood stunt woman, who makes her living falling down stairs and other dangerous tasks as a double for Hollywood stars. It also takes a look at a collection of early-American transportation vehicles and a skilled ivory carver.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?632591</url></doc>
